The input array `candiesCount` must not be null.
The length of `candiesCount` must be greater than or equal to 1.
The elements of `candiesCount` must be positive integers.
The input array `queries` must not be null.
The length of `queries` must be greater than or equal to 1.
Each element of `queries` must be an array of length 3.
The first element of each query must be a valid index in `candiesCount`.
The second element of each query must be a non-negative integer.
The third element of each query must be a positive integer.
